* End-to-End Tests
** Purpose
***_ Simulate complete workflows
***_ Validate entire pipeline output
** Test Pattern
***_ Setup test inputs
***_ Execute full pipeline
***_ Verify final output/counts
***_ Cleanup test data
** Characteristics
***_ Realistic business scenarios
***_ Longer execution time
** Scheduling
***_ Run during off-peak hours
***_ Part of deployment pipeline
***_ Not on every code change
@endmindmap
